casebody.data:
Ulysses T. WARE, applicant,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 14A1194 (14-8628). Supreme Court of the United States July 20, 2015. Application to file a petition for rehearing in excess of page limit addressed to THE CHIEF JUSTICE and referred to the Court denied. Justice SOTAMAYOR took no part in the consideration or decision of this application.
